com.epoch.translations

Class QSetAllTranslns

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epoch.translations.QSetAllTranslns

  • public final class QSetAllTranslns
extends Object
    Utility class containing static methods for writing or retrieving all of the translations of a question set header, or for retrieving all of the translations of a single question's statement, question data, and evaluators. Used when cloning a question and in import/export.
